how%2F119596872.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119596872.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESalman%20Khan%20returns%20in%20his%20action-packed%20role%20for%20'Sikandar'%2C%20directed%20by%20AR%20Murugadoss%2C%20set%20to%20release%20on%20Eid.%20Despite%20physical%20tolls%2C%20he%20remains%20committed%20to%20the%20genre%20and%20discusses%20collaboration%20with%20South%20filmmakers%20and%20theater%20affordability.%20He%20also%20comments%20on%20the%20upcoming%20box%20office%20clash%20with%20'Empuraan'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20Clears%20Bill%20To%20Modernise%20And%20Consolidate%20Immigration%20Laws%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20passed%20the%20Immigration%20and%20Foreigners%20Bill%2C%202025%20after%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20proposed%20law%20that%20will%20modernise%20and%20consolidate%20India's%20immigration%20laws.%20Junior%20Home%20Minister%20Nityanand%20Rai%20introduced%20the%20bill%20on%20behalf%20of%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20a%20three-hour-long%20discussion%20on%20the%20bill%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20India%20welcomes%20those%20who%20come%20here%20to%20help%20in%20development%2C%20but%20those%20who%20come%20to%20create%20trouble%2C%20whether%20Rohingya%20or%20Bangladeshis%2C%20will%20face%20strong%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20will%20also%20help%20in%20identifying%20those%20who%20come%20here%20with%20bad%20intentions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20cleared%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20once%20it%20becomes%20an%20Act%2C%20will%20help%20in%20tackling%20illegal%20immigration%20into%20India%20and%20facilitate%20tracking%20of%20movement%20of%20foreigners%20who%20overstay%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20cited%20Indians%20who%20went%20abroad%20and%20left%20a%20huge%20positive%20impact%20in%20the%20countries%20they%20settled%20in%2C%20and%20called%20for%20a%20legal%20framework%20for%20India%20as%20well%20to%20ensure%20those%20who%20come%20to%20India%20for%20good%20work%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20nation's%20development%20feel%20welcomed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20important.%20The%20main%20issue%20is%20that%20immigration%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20subject%2C%20but%20is%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20linked%20to%20various%20issues.%20The%20bill%20will%20ensure%20a%20close%20monitoring%20of%20everyone%20who%20visits%20India%2C%20why%20they%20visit%20India%2C%20and%20how%20long%20they%20want%20to%20stay.%20It%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%20to%20know%20the%20details%20of%20every%20foreigner%20visiting%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20after%20over%20a%20three-hour-long%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20security%20point%20of%20view%2C%20this%20law%20will%20fight%20against%20drug%20cartels%2C%20infiltrators%2C%20arms%20smugglers%2C%20and%20those%20who%20want%20to%20destroy%20India's%20economy%20from%20within%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20law%20empowers%20the%20central%20government%20to%20exert%20control%20over%20places%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bfrequented%20by%20any%20foreigner%26quot%3B%20and%20order%20the%20owners%20to%20close%20the%20premises%2C%20allow%20its%20use%20under%20specified%20conditions%2C%20or%20refuse%20admission%20to%20all%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecified%20class%26quot%3B%20of%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatters%20linked%20to%20foreigners%20and%20immigration%20are%20presently%20administered%20through%20four%20laws%20-%20Passport%20(Entry%20into%20India)%20Act%2C%201920%3B%20the%20Registration%20of%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%201939%3B%20the%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%201946%2C%20and%20the%20Immigration%20(Carriers'%20Liability)%20Act%2C%202000.%20All%20these%20laws%20are%20now%20proposed%20to%20be%20repealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Immigration%20and%20Foreigners%20Bill%2C%202025%20consists%20of%20several%20existing%20provisions%20in%20the%20four%20laws%20proposed%20to%20be%20repealed%20after%20simplification%20and%20harmonisation%2C%20it%20also%20has%20certain%20new%20provisions%20to%20meet%20today's%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seeks%20to%20balance%20the%20requirements%20of%20national%20security%20and%20related%20issues%20of%20immigration%20with%20the%20need%20to%20promote%20economic%20growth%20and%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20law%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20connected%20with%20matters%20related%20to%20giving%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743082440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9mga7t98_lok-sabha-generic-ani-_625x300_26_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-clears-bill-to-modernise-and-consolidate-immigration-laws-8024737%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20passed%20the%20Immigration%20and%20Foreigners%20Bill%2C%202025%20after%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20proposed%20law%20that%20will%20modernise%20and%20consolidate%20India's%20immigration%20laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-clears-bill-to-modernise-and-consolidate-immigration-laws-8024737%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salman-Abhishek%2C%20Aishwarya%2C%20Prabhas-Anushka%3A%20Top%205%20news%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743082200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119596122%2Cimgsize-61810.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2F