20Store%20apps%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e52a70b8b41a9673fbd4b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22858%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Utah%20law%20puts%20the%20onus%20on%20Google's%20and%20Apple's%20app%20stores%20to%20verify%20user%20ages.%3Cp%3EApp%20Store%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUtah%20just%20passed%20a%20law%20that%20would%20make%20app%20stores%20verify%20user%20ages%20instead%20of%20individual%20apps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20and%20Google%20would%20have%20to%20get%20parental%20consent%20before%20minors%20can%20download%20certain%20apps%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%2C%20Snap%2C%20and%20X%20praised%20the%20bill.%20Google%20and%20Apple%20have%20said%20it%20raises%20privacy%20concerns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUtah%20just%20became%20the%20first%20state%20to%20pass%20a%20law%20that%20makes%20app%20stores%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20individual%20apps%20%E2%80%94%20responsible%20for%20verifying%20user%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20and%20Apple%2C%20the%20tech%20giants%20behind%20the%20two%20main%20app%20stores%2C%20have%20opposed%20the%20bill.%20But%20Meta%2C%20Snap%2C%20and%20X%20have%20praised%20the%20law%2C%20which%20Utah%20Gov.%20Spencer%20Cox%20signed%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20App%20Store%20Accountability%20Act%2C%20also%20known%20as%20S.B.%20142%2C%20is%20set%20to%20take%20effect%20on%20May%207%20%E2%80%94%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20legal%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20requires%20Apple%20and%20Google%20to%20confirm%20the%20age%20of%20anyone%20who%20creates%20an%20account%20in%20Utah.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf%20that%20person%20is%20under%2018%2C%20the%20account%20must%20be%20linked%20to%20a%20parent%20or%20verified%20with%20extra%20documentation.%20Parents%20must%20also%20approve%20in-app%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20represents%20a%20major%20shift%20in%20how%20states%20regulate%20child%20safety%20online.%20Instead%20of%20directly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-apple-feud-app-store-child-teen-mental-health-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etargeting%20social%20media%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lawmakers%20in%20Utah%20have%20focused%20on%20the%20gatekeepers%3A%20app%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupporters%20say%20the%20law%20gives%20parents%20more%20centralized%20control%20over%20what%20their%20kids%20can%20download%2C%20a%20change%20that%20major%20social%20media%20companies%20have%20been%20pushing%20for.%20Meta%2C%20Snap%2C%20and%20X%20%E2%80%94%20three%20companies%20under%20growing%20pressure%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-internal-report-shows-instagram-bad-for-teens-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotect%20teens%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20welcomed%20the%20law%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParents%20want%20a%20one-stop-shop%20to%20oversee%20and%20approve%20the%20many%20apps%20their%20teens%20want%20to%20download%2C%20and%20Utah%20has%20led%20the%20way%20in%20centralizing%20it%20within%20a%20device's%20app%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20approach%20spares%20users%20from%20repeatedly%20submitting%20personal%20information%20to%20countless%20individual%20apps%20and%20online%20services.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20verification%20bill%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-apple-teen-safety-laws-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-running%20turf%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Meta%20and%20Apple%20over%20data%20practices%2C%20platform%20control%2C%20and%20even%20smart%20glasses.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMeta%20has%20pushed%20for%20app%20stores%20to%20take%20the%20lead%20on%20age%20restrictions%2C%20while%20Apple%20says%20it%20raises%20privacy%20concerns.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%