A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc9847mr0746o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Funding%20Cut%20Could%20Cause%20'Over%20A%20Million%20Deaths'%3A%20Vaccine%20Alliance%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20cutting%20funding%20to%20Gavi%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20provides%20vaccines%20to%20the%20world's%20poorest%20countries%2C%20could%20result%20in%20more%20than%20a%20million%20deaths%20and%20will%20endanger%20lives%20everywhere%2C%20the%20group's%20CEO%20warned%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20that%20Washington%20is%20planning%20to%20end%20funding%20for%20Gavi%2C%20first%20reported%20in%20the%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20comes%20as%20the%20two-month-old%20administration%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20aggressively%20slashes%20foreign%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20included%20in%20a%20281-page%20spreadsheet%20that%20the%20severely%20downsized%20United%20States%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20sent%20to%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavi's%20chief%20executive%20Sania%20Nishtar%20told%20AFP%20the%20alliance%20had%20%26quot%3Bnot%20received%20a%20termination%20notice%20from%20the%20US%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20was%20%26quot%3Bengaging%20with%20the%20White%20House%20and%20Congress%20with%20a%20view%20to%20securing%20%24300%20million%20approved%20by%20Congress%20for%20our%202025%20activities%20and%20longer-term%20funding%26quot%3B%2C%20Nishtar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20cut%20in%20Gavi's%20funding%20from%20the%20US%20would%20have%20a%20disastrous%20impact%20on%20global%20health%20security%2C%20potentially%20resulting%20in%20over%20a%20million%20deaths%20from%20preventable%20diseases%20and%20endangering%20lives%20everywhere%20from%20dangerous%20disease%20outbreaks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20experts%20and%20organisations%20have%20warned%20that%20cutting%20Gavi's%20funding%20would%20ultimately%20cost%20the%20world%20more%20money%20and%20set%20back%20a%20quarter-century%20of%20progress%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20many%20deadly%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Nuzzo%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20epidemiology%20at%20Brown%20University%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bmind-bogglingly%20short-sighted%20proposal%26quot%3B%20would%20have%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%20consequences%20for%20the%20health%20of%20children%20everywhere%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20support%20for%20Gavi's%20vaccination%20efforts%20is%20not%20charity%20--%20it's%20a%20cost-effective%20investment%20to%20prevent%20deadly%20and%20costly%20outbreaks%20that%20can%20come%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Cruel'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavi%20says%20it%20helps%20vaccinate%20more%20than%20half%20the%20world's%20children%20against%20infectious%20diseases%20including%20Covid-19%2C%20Ebola%2C%20malaria%2C%20rabies%2C%20polio%2C%20cholera%2C%20tuberculosis%20(TB)%2C%20typhoid%20and%20yellow%20fever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20currently%20provides%20around%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20budget%20of%20Gavi%2C%20a%20public-private%20partnership%20headquartered%20in%20Geneva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20Elliman%2C%20a%20child%20health%20researcher%20at%20University%20College%20London%2C%20said%20cutting%20funding%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20only%20cruel%2C%20but%20is%20not%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20anyone%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20diseases%20such%20as%20measles%20and%20TB%20increase%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%2C%20it%20is%20a%20hazard%20to%20us%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20Science%20Media%20Centre%2C%20adding%20that%20measles%20was%20already%20rising%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Europe%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20sweeping%20aid%20cuts%2C%20%26quot%3Binstitutions%20are%20reluctant%20to%20speak%20out%20in%20case%20they%20are%20targeted%20and%20individuals%20are%20self-censoring%20to%20protect%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Andrew%20Pollard%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Oxford%20Vaccine%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20moral%20case%20for%20supporting%20the%20remarkable%20global%20health%20efforts%20that%20help%20the%20poor%20of%20the%20world%2C%20but%20also%20remember%20that%20it%20is%20in%20our%20own%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20reminds%20us%2C%20infectious%20diseases%20cross%20borders%20and%20put%20all%20of%20us%20at%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20Will%20Regret%20This'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20health%20researchers%20also%20said%20the%20cuts%20would%20be%20a%20poor%20return%20on%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20%241%20spent%20on%20vaccinations%20in%20developing%20countries%20where%20Gavi%20operates%2C%20%2421%20will%20be%20saved%20this%20decade%20in%20%26quot%3Bhealth%20care%20costs%2C%20lost%20wages%20and%20lost%20productivity%20from%20illness%20and%20death%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20vaccine%20group%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20the%20Johns%20Hopkins%20Bloomberg%20School%20of%20Public%20Health%20recently%20found%20that%20costs%20averted%20by%20vaccine%20programmes%20in%2073%20countries%20will%20add%20up%20to%20nearly%20%24782%20billion%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECraig%20Spencer%2C%20a%20doctor%20and%20Ebola%20survivor%20at%20Brown%20University%2C%20said%20the%20loss%20of%20US%20support%20to%20Gavi%20means%20%26quot%3Bkids%20will%20die%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20warned%20that%20Gavi%20maintains%20the%20global%20stockpile%20of%20vaccines%20for%20diseases%20including%20Ebola%2C%20cholera%2C%20yellow%20fever%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20regret%20this%2C%26quot%3B