%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20suspect%20the%20Lloyd%20Fireplace's%20perceived%20size%20and%20stature%20will%20very%20much%20be%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20beholder%20%E2%80%94%20depending%20on%20which%20room%20it%20ends%20up%20in.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20noticed%20some%20comments%20online%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20smaller%20than%20they%20thought%20it%20would%20be.%20But%20the%20first%20words%20from%20my%20wife%20were%20about%20how%20it%20was%20a%20little%20bigger%20than%20she%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20its%20dimensions%20of%2025.5%20inches%20round%20and%2043.5%20inches%20tall%20ahead%20of%20time%20so%20seeing%20it%20in%20person%20didn't%20surprise%20me.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20curious%20whether%20it%20would%20actually%20look%20substantial%20enough%20in%20our%20living%20room%20with%20high%20ceilings.%20We%20positioned%20it%20between%20two%20accent%20chairs%20and%20we%20were%20both%20satisfied%20with%20its%20appearance.%20It's%20not%20the%20main%20focal%20point%2C%20but%20we%20also%20weren't%20aiming%20for%20it%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutting%20it%20in%20a%20smaller%20room%20will%20give%20it%20a%20bigger%20presence%20but%20I%20think%20it%20can%20find%20a%20spot%20in%20most%20areas.%20It's%20versatile%20enough%20to%20nestle%20in%20a%20living%20room%2C%20but%20small%20enough%20to%20fit%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20a%20primary%20bedroom%20if%20you%20want%20to%20go%20that%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20size%2C%20it%20has%20an%20unquestionably%20mid-century%20design.%20If%20you%20add%20in%20the%20option%20to%20pick%20a%20bold%20orange%20or%20baby%20blue%20color%20buyers%20can%20give%20it%20a%20real%20funkiness%20if%20they%20want%20that.%20I%20went%20with%20the%20more%20neutral%20Mist%20color%20that%20I%20think%20is%20non-descript%20enough%20to%20work%20in%20most%20homes%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20decor%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260189f86-073e-40e2-826f-5cf7cee927e5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESet%20up%20was%20quick%20and%20uncomplicated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222576%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solo%20Stove%20Lloyd%20fireplace%20next%20to%20window%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e323f669253ccddf9a49bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Solo%20Stove%20fireplace%20assembly%20took%20about%2015%20minutes.%20The%20three%20main%20parts%20are%20the%20the%20base%2C%20fireplace%20area%2C%20and%20top%20pipe.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people's%20first%20thought%2C%20when%20they%20see%20the%20Lloyd%20Modern%20Fireplace%2C%20is%20probably%20something%20cozy%20and%20relaxing%2C%20not%20worrying%20about%20assembling%20the%20product%20when%20it%20arrives.%20While%20it%20does%20need%20to%20be%20put%20together%2C%20the%20good%20news%20is%20that%20it%20doesn't%20take%20very%20long.%20The%20assembly%20process%20took%20about%2015%20minutes%20by%20myself.%20There%20are%20three%20parts%20to%20the%20external%20frame%3A%20the%20base%2C%20main%20area%2C%20and%20top%20pipe.%20Those%20pieces%20attach%20with%20a%20total%20of%20five%20screws.%20Once%20those%20are%20connected%2C%20the%20internal%20area%20that%20holds%20the%20fuel%20cans%20drops%20down%20into%20an%20opening%20and%20sits%20securely%20without%20any%20additional%20attachments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20round%20out%20the%20finished%20product%20there's%20a%20glass%20divider%20that%20stands%20upright%20just%20by%20sliding%20it%20into%20its%20slot.%20Then%20four%20rubber%20feet%20hook%20onto%20the%20base%20and%20feature%20a%20small%20magnet%20to%20keep%20them%20from%20sliding%20around.%20Not%20only%20is%20the%20assembly%20process%20easy%20enough%20for%20nearly%20anyone%2C%20but%20it's%20deceptively%20simple.%20At%20the%20completion%2C%20I%20was%20briefly%20left%20wondering%20if%20that%20could%20really%20be%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fireplace%20comes%20with%20six%20cans%20of%20gel%20fuel%2C%20but%20you'll%20certainly%20want%20to%20buy%20more%20than%20that.%20My%20cans%20arrived%20later%20than%20the%20fireplace%20so%20I%20had%20extra%20time%20to%20inspect%20the%20snuffer%20that's%20included%20in%20the%20box.%20One%20side%20of%20the%20tool%20is%20a%20thin%2C%20narrow%20piece%20of%20metal%20used%20for%20prying%20the%20fuel%20can%20open%2C%20the%20way%20you%20would%20a%20can%20of%20paint.%20On%20the%20other%20side%20is%20a%20magnet%20to%20lift%20the%20lids%20off%20the%20fuel%20and%20then%20place%20them%20back%20on%2C%20to%20snuff%20the%20flames%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22snuffing%20out%20a%20flame%20on%20the%20Solo%20Stove%20Lloyd%20fireplace%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e3234863d72727e1983c23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20included%20snuffer%20makes%20it%20safe%20and%20easy%20to%20extinguish%20flames%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20obvious%20place%20to%20keep%20it%20when%20not%20in%20use.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20not%20an%20obvious%20spot%20to%20store%20the%20lids%20and%20snuffer%20while%20the%20fireplace%20is%20being%20used.%20I'm%20also%20not%20sure%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20have%20a%20hidden%20spot%20on%20the%20unit%20itself%20because%20of%20the%20heat.%20So%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20you%20will%20need%20to%20find%20a%20place%20for%20the%20three%20lids%20and%20a%20metal%20tool%20during%20its%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255356e9e-c757-4264-ae99-24913b5415f6%5C%22%3EIt%20adds%20warmth%20and%20coziness%20to%20any%20space%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20things%20that%20people%20might%20want%20the%20Lloyd%20Modern%20Fireplace%20to%20be%2C%20its%20primary%20objective%20is%20probably%20a%20heater.%20You%20may%20want%20it%20for%20its%20appearance%2C%20but%20it's%20built%20around%20burning%20fuel%20and%20producing%20real%20flames.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20the%20fireplace's%20design%20may%20suggest%20it%20shoots%20its%20heat%20out%20of%20its%20front%2C%20wide%20mouth%2C%20opening%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't.%20Most%20of%20the%20heat%20is%20funneled%20up%20through%20its%20top%20pipe%20opening.%20The%20front%20area%20isn't%20void%20of%20heat%2C%20but%20if%20you%20need%20immediate%20relief%20from%20a%20chill%20then%20your%20best%20bet%20is%20to%20hover%20over%20the%20top%20of%20it.%20There's%20only%20a%20light%20warmth%20from%20the%20front%20that%20can%20be%20appreciated%20over%20an%20extended%20time%20spent%20in%20front%20of%20it%2C%20rather%20than%20mere%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20can%20of%20the%20smokeless%20gel%20fuel%20is%20advertised%20as%20producing%203%2C000%20BTUs%20of%20heat.%20With%20three%20cans%20burning%20at%20once%2C%20for%20a%20total%20of%209%2C000%20BTUs%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20fireplace%20produced%20a%20satisfactory%20amount%20of%20heat%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20upwards.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20of%20burning%2C%20our%20living%20area%20had%20an%20overall%20warmth%20to%20it%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20more%20open%20and%20expansive%20room.%20The%20warming%20effect%20is%20much%20quicker%20in%20rooms%20with%20lower%20ceilings%20or%20a%20smaller%20footprint.%20Be%20aware%2C%20that%20while%20the%20base%20stays%20cooler%20to%20the%20touch%2C%20the%20middle%20and%20top%20areas%20do%20get%20hot%20so%20you'll%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20young%20kids%20won't%20have%20easy%20access%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20factors%20to%20consider%20for%20heating%20a%20room%2C%20from%20insulation%2C%20number%20of%20windows%2C%20and%20ceiling%20height%20to%20where%20you%20live%20and%20the%20climate.%20Everyone's%20home%20is%20different%20but%20you%20can%20try%20to%20get%20an%20estimate%20of%20your%20needs%20based%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculator.net%2Fbtu-calculator.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBTU%20calculator%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%209.000%20BTUs%20is%20overkill%2C%20you%20can%20reduce%20the%20heat%20by%20only%20lighting%20one%20or%20two%20cans%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223390fad6-0477-464a-bafe-96b492afab93%5C%22%3EIt's%20truly%20smokeless%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solo%20Stove%20Lloyd%20fireplace%20lit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e32348b8b41a9673fbafee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20the%20ambiance%20of%20a%20crackling%20fire%2C%20none%20of%20the%20smoke.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20wondering%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20a%20hint%20of%20smoke.%20It's%20advertised%20as%20being%20smokeless%20and%20it%20is.%20You%20will%20get%20crackling%20sounds%20from%20the%20gel%20fuel%2C%20but%20I%20consider%20that%20a%20positive.%20It's%20not%20exactly%20the%20same%20noise%20as%20a%20wood-burning%20fire%2C%20but%20it's%20close.%20I%20thought%20the%20auditory%20ambiance%20matched%20the%20visual%20delight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20able%20to%20try%20the%20Lloyd%20Fireplace%20outside%2C%20because%20of%20a%20rainy%20spell%2C%20but%20it%20is%20promoted%20as%20suitable%20for%20indoors%20or%20out.%20It%20would%20be%20a%20great%20visual%20fixture%20for%20a%20back%20patio%20too.%20But%20based%20on%20indoor%20performance%2C%20I%20would%20expect%20its%20heat%20impact%20to%20be%20even%20more%20limited%20when%20outside.%20I%20wouldn't%20count%20on%20being%20able%20to%20huddle%20up%20in%20front%20of%20it%20to%20save%20you%20from%20some%20chilly%20night%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b047912-f859-4733-a672-b6c273d8f234%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20the%20most%20efficient%20way%20to%20warm%20up%20a%20space%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22smokeless%20gel%20fuel%20that%20goes%20on%20firepla%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e32348b8b41a9673fbafef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222405%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEach%20smokeless%20gel%20fuel%20canister%20can%20burn%20for%20three%20hours.%20They%20cost%20about%20%2440%20for%20six%2C%20and%20the%20fireplace%20uses%20three%20at%20a%20time.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20used%20the%20fireplace%20in%20the%20primary%20bedroom%20to%20compare%20the%20differences%2C%20the%20heating%20effect%20was%20significantly%20more%20noticeable.%20One%20thing%20to%20consider%20regarding%20the%20heat%20is%20that%20there%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20more%20efficient%20ways%20to%20stay%20warm%20through%20the%20winter%20months.%20The%20fireplace%20is%20much%20more%20than%20decorative%2C%20but%20you're%20buying%20this%20because%20you%20want%20the%20glow%20of%20real%20flames%20and%20an%20eye-catching%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20factors%20around%20efficiency%20includes%20the%20expensive%20fuel%20cans%20that%20last%20for%20about%20three%20hours.%20For%20reference%2C%20Solo%20Stove%20sells%20a%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Ddb870837fca025664f0b5ec099c76b7ea3b323d23785e2434b55fb573efdde6e%26postID%3D67e320b6e2041f80933adbeb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fsolo-stove-lloyd-modern-fireplace-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.solostove.com%252Fen-us%252Fp%252Fpure-gel-fuel%253Fsku%253DSSPURE-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix-pack%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20non-toxic%20gel%20fuel%20cans%20for%20%2439.99.%20I%20easily%20went%20through%20the%20first%20six%20cans%20in%20a%20weekend.%20That's%20two%20nights%20of%20an%20evening%20fire.%20Even%20if%20you%20scaled%20back%20to%20an%20hour%20each%20night%20you%20could%20be%20looking%20at%20%2440%20a%20week%20to%20get%20the%20full%20experience.%20There%20are%20other%20brands%20of%20gel%20fuel%20you%20can%20buy%2C%20but%20in%20my%20searches%2C%20they're%20not%20much%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221213a499-5c77-4a7f-b03f-fb9c0f19eab0%5C%22%3EThe%20fuel%20cans%20do%20emit%20a%20smell%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20far%20the%20most%20divisive%20aspect%20of%20the%20fireplace%20will%20be%20its%20smell%20when%20lit.%20The%20Lloyd%20Modern%20Fireplace%20has%20its%20subjective%20characteristics%20like%20size%2C%20style%2C%20and%20heat%20output%20%E2%80%94%20is%20it%20warm%20enough%20for%20your%20home%20or%20room%3F%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20smell%20at%20least%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20a%20showstopper%20for%20some%20people.%20To%20my%20nose%2C%20the%20light%20aroma%20I%20smelled%20when%20opening%20the%20non-toxic%20fuel%20can%20was%20one%20of%20rubbing%20alcohol%20or%20something%20in%20that%20vein.%20It%20wasn't%20offensive%2C%20but%20also%20didn't%20strike%20joy.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20sterile%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20be%20clear%20that%20while%20a%20consideration%2C%20the%20smell%20won't%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20everyone.%20If%20I%20hadn't%20read%20some%20comments%20ahead%20of%20time%20mentioning%20they%20thought%20the%20odor%20from%20the%20burning%20gel%20fuel%20was%20strong%2C%20I%20might%20not%20have%20had%20it%20on%20my%20radar.%20I%20got%20whiffs%20of%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20clinical%20smell%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20but%20in%20general%2C%20it%20just%20wasn't%20something%20glaring%20to%20me.%20It%20was%20mostly%20when%20I%20heard%20from%20others%20in%20my%20family%20that%20they%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20strong%20that%20I%20examined%20it%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20having%20it%20in%20a%20room%20with%20high%20ceilings%20dissipated%20the%20smell%20more%20than%20if%20it%20was%20in%20a%20smaller%20space.%20But%20I%20also%20don't%20know%20that%20for%20sure.%20In%20trying%20to%20pinpoint%20more%20context%2C%20I%20didn't%20particularly%20notice%20a%20pattern%20of%20whether%20burning%20the%20gel%20for%20longer%20created%20more%20of%20a%