ogram%20will%20change%20or%20stop%26quot%3B%20and%20described%20the%20F-35%20as%20a%20joint%20effort%2C%20a%20jet%20%26quot%3Bdeveloped%2C%20deployed%20and%20maintained%20as%20a%20common%20platform%20based%20on%20a%20strong%20partnership%20with%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGermany%20and%20the%20UK%20have%20also%20said%20they%20remain%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EF-35s%20are%20considered%20among%20the%20world's%20most%20advanced%20jets%2C%20and%20changing%20jet%20type%20would%20create%20additional%20work%20that%20could%20delay%20readiness%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Europe%20is%20increasingly%20worried%20about%20threats%20from%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20there%20are%20signs%20that%20many%20countries%20are%20questioning%20their%20long-term%20dependency%20on%20US%20tech%20and%20weaponry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20of%20Sweden%2C%20which%20doesn't%20operate%20F-35s%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Farticles%2F2025-03-20%2Fswedens-prime-minister-says-that-buying-us-weapons-is-not-a-security-risk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20this%20month%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20doesn't%20view%20US%20weaponry%20as%20a%20security%20threat%2C%20but%20said%20Sweden%20and%20Europe%20%26quot%3Bwould%20do%20well%20from%20being%20a%20little%20less%20dependent%20on%20the%20US%20defense%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrance-seizing-chance-trump-allies-question-f35-jet-europe-opportunity-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743076029000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e2c29e63d72727e1982c31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrance-seizing-chance-trump-allies-question-f35-jet-europe-opportunity-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20actions%20have%20ca