cs%20has%20brought%20the%20RSS%20not%20only%20power%20but%20also%20a%20unique%20kind%20of%20challenge.%20While%20it%20has%20gained%20respect%20and%20legitimacy%20among%20a%20large%20section%20of%20Hindu%20society%2C%20it%20has%20also%20faced%20criticism%20for%20its%20perceived%20exclusive%20and%20divisive%20agenda.%20Despite%20achieving%20global%20recognition%20and%20exponential%20growth%2C%20it%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20harbouring%20an%20anti-Muslim%20stance.%20Now%2C%20it%20seems%20the%20RSS%20has%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20step%20back%20to%20prepare%20for%20its%20next%20leap%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Events%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20the%20recently%20held%20RSS%20Pratinidhi%20Sabha%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%20assumes%20great%20importance.%20Two%20key%20developments%20have%20emerged%20that%20will%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20the%20RSS's%20trajectory.%20First%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20set%20to%20meet%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20in%20Nagpur%20on%20March%2030%2C%20marking%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%20since%20becoming%20Prime%20Minister.%20Second%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20appoint%20its%20next%20party%20president%20supposedly%20because%20of%20RSS%20pressure.%20JP%20Nadda%20continues%20as%20president%20despite%20being%20burdened%20with%20two%20additional%20responsibilities%3A%20serving%20as%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20and%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20These%20two%20events%20are%20closely%20interlinked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20becoming%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Modi%20has%20centralised%20government%20machinery%20and%20is%20seen%20to%20have%20monopolised%20the%20party%20structure.%20The%20BJP%2C%20once%20known%20for%20collective%20decision-making%20even%20under%20stalwarts%20like%20Vajpayee%20and%20Advani%2C%20has%20seen%20that%20space%20shrink%20under%20Modi's%20leadership.%20Much%20like%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20Modi%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20the%20party%2C%20leaving%20no%20room%20for%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20RSS%20Feels%20Sidelined%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20perceived%20monopolisation%20has%20left%20even%20the%20top%20RSS%20leadership%20feeling%20sidelined.%20Within%20the%20Hindutva%20fold%2C%20it%20was%20openly%20debated%20that%20Bhagwat%20had%20little%20influence.%20Nadda%20even%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20become%20self-sufficient%2C%20implying%20it%20no%20longer%20needed%20the%20RSS%20to%20win%20elections.%20Whispers%20within%20the%20Hindutva%20fold%20suggested%20that%20the%20RSS%20ensured%20that%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20secure%20a%20parliamentary%20majority%20in%202024%2C%20reducing%20the%20party%20to%20240%20seats.%20The%20BJP's%20failure%20to%20appoint%20Nadda's%20successor%20was%20attributed%20to%20Bhagwat's%20insistence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%20visit%20to%20Nagpur%20signals%20a%20truce%20and%20reaffirms%20the%20RSS%20chief's%20supremacy%20within%20the%20Hindutva%20fold.%20Modi%2C%20an%20RSS%20%3Cem%3Epracharak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(worker)%20loaned%20to%20politics%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20was%20tasked%20with%20strengthening%20the%20BJP.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20this%20meeting%20will%20finalise%20the%20name%20of%20the%20next%20party%20president%20and%20establish%20a%20new%20protocol%20to%20restore%20the%20RSS's%20influence%20over%20the%20BJP's%20internal%20functioning.%20Although%20publicly%2C%20the%20RSS%20denies%20involvement%20in%20politics%20or%20control%20over%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20different.%20It%20monitors%20and%20micromanages%20the%20party%20through%20its%20volunteers.%20During%20Modi's%20first%20decade%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20RSS%20lost%20this%20control%2C%20causing%20discontent%20among%20its%20leadership.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20hope%20for%20equilibrium%20to%20be%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Stance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20is%20also%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20BJP's%20overtly%20aggressive%20and%20rabid%20anti-Muslim%20stance%2C%20at%20least%20of%20some%20leaders.%20The%202024%20parliamentary%20election%20was%20the%20most%20communally%20charged%20one%20in%20history.%20Despite%20all%20attempts%20to%20polarise%2C%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20get%20the%20majority%20mark%20on%20its%20own.%20Bhagwat%20has%20advocated%20moderation%2C%20making%20statements%20like%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20Muslims%2C%20Hindutva%20is%20incomplete%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20DNA%20of%20everyone%20in%20this%20country%20is%20the%20same%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%20search%20for%20Shivlings%20in%20every%20mosque%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20remarks%20invited%20ridicule%20from%20some%20Hindutva%20volunteers%2C%20who%20openly%20criticised%20and%20abused%20Bhagwat%20on%20social%20media%E2%80%94a%20shocking%20development%20given%20the%20reverence%20traditionally%20accorded%20to%20the%20RSS%20chief.%20The%20RSS%20is%20aware%20that%20a%20section%20of%20its%20volunteers%20has%20become%20so%20radicalised%20that%20they%20are%20breaching%20organisational%20discipline%2C%20a%20source%20of%20pride%20for%20the%20RSS.%20If%20this%20trend%20is%20not%20curbed%2C%20the%20leadership%20risks%20being%20hijacked%20by%20extreme%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20RSS%20is%20ready%20to%20compromise%20on%20the%20core%20of%20its%20ideology.%20It%20seeks%20only%20a%20tactical%20retreat%20to%20consolidate%20its%20gains%20and%20prepare%20the%20organisation%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%2C%20for%20its%20next%20leap.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20cool%20down%20communal%20tensions%20and%20project%20an%20image%20of%20being%20non-confrontational.%20The%20RSS%20aspires%20to%20engage%20with%20every%20section%20of%20society.%20It%20is%20not%20opposed%20to%20Muslims%20and%20believes%20in%20reconciliation.%20It%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%2C%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20it%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20issue%20of%20Aurangzeb%20is%20not%20relevant%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExternal%20Risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20has%20also%20recognised%20that%20the%20ideological%20march%20of%20Hindutva%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20has%20exposed%20new%20fault%20lines.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20infused%20fresh%20energy%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9CSave%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D%20campaign%20and%20the%20caste%20census%20debate.%20The%20movement%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20permanently%20alienate%20Dalits%20from%20the%20Hindutva%20narrative.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20caste%20census%20debate%20has%20reopened%20the%20wounds%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%2C%20giving%20new%20life%20to%20the%20social%20justice%20agenda.%20If%20Gandhi%2C%20along%20with%20OBC%20leaders%20from%20Mandal%20parties%2C%20succeeds%20in%20transforming%20the%20social%20justice%20debate%20into%20a%20movement%2C%20it%20could%20not%20only%20harm%20the%20BJP%20electorally%20but%20also%20jeopardise%20the%20RSS's%20Hindu%20unity%20project.%20It%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20organisation%20has%20conceded%20that%20a%20caste%20census%20can%20be%20conducted%2C%20but%20only%20for%20welfare%20purposes%2C%20not%20for%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20North-South%20divide%20has%20also%20alarmed%20the%20RSS.%20The%20issues%20of%20delimitation%20and%20the%20three-language%20formula%20have%20brought%20the%20North-South%20debate%20back%20to%20the%20forefront%20of%20national%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuture%2C%20Not%20Present%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20century%2C%20the%20RSS%20has%20reached%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20its%20success.%20It%20has%20thrived%20where%20its%20ideological%20counterparts%2C%20such%20as%20socialists%20and%20communists%2C%20have%20faltered%20and%20are%20now%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20extinction.%20The%20RSS's%20success%20lies%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20blend%20ideology%20with%20pragmatism.%20The%20RSS%20understands%20that%20its%20%E2%80%9Cone%20nation%2C%20one%20culture%E2%80%9D%20project%20is%20a%20civilisational%20endeavour%20that%20will%20take%20centuries%20to%20achieve%2C%20not%20just%20one%20or%20two%20generations.%20For%20Modi%2C%20the%20next%20election%20may%20be%20the%20immediate%20goal%2C%20but%20for%20Bhagwat%2C%20elections%20are%20important%20yet%20something%20that%20can%20be%20sacrificed%20for%20the%20larger%20cause%20of%20Hindu%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bhagwat-Modi%20meeting%20is%20about%20shaping%20the%20future%2C%20not%20addressing%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0SatyaHindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743072960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fo6i4gfrg_modi-bhagwat_625x300_27_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-a-modi-bhagwat-meet-can-tell-you-about-rss-plans-8023512%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20Modi%2C%20the%20next%20election%20may%20be%20the%20immediate%20goal%2C%20but%20for%20Bhagwat%2C%20elections%20are%20important%20yet%20something%20that%20can%20be%20sacrificed%20for%20the%20larger%20cause%20of%20Hindu%20unity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-a-modi-bhagwat-meet-can-tell-you-about-rss-plans-8023512%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20made%20a%20big%20tax%20mistake%20when%20I%20filed%20my%20taxes%20this%20year%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20but%20this%20time%2C%20I'm%20doing%20it%20again%20on%20purpose%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time