the%20ruling%20DMK%20and%20the%20main%20Opposition%20AIADMK%2C%20have%20started%20building%20their%20election%20planks.%20The%20DMK%20has%20stepped%20up%20its%20offensive%20against%20the%20Centre%2C%20playing%20up%20the%20delimitation%20issue%20and%20challenging%20the%20three-language%20push%20in%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy.%20The%20AIADMK%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20cautiously%20identifying%20its%20poll%20partners%20to%20prevent%20another%20drubbing%20in%20the%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20two%20days%20after%20AIADMK%20leader%20E%20Palaniswami%20met%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20sparking%20speculation%20about%20another%20AIADMK-BJP%20alliance%2C%20AIADMK%20today%20supported%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20resolution%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20which%20the%20Opposition%20has%20challenged%20in%20Parliament.%20The%20four%20MLAs%20of%20the%20BJP%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Assembly%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20bring%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20Waqf%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEPS'%20Mixed%20Signals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Mr%20Palaniswami%20met%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20sparking%20a%20buzz%20over%20a%20poll%20alliance%20between%20AIADMK%20and%20BJP%2C%20which%20have%20joined%20forces%20multiple%20times%20earlier.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20leader%20said%20any%20decision%20on%20alliance%20will%20be%20taken%20closer%20to%20the%20polls.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20politics%2C%20as%20per%20the%20political%20situation%2C%20changes%20will%20happen.%20How%20can%20we%20tell%20now%3F%20When%20did%20we%20form%20an%20alliance%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%202019%20election%3F%20It%20was%20in%20February%20when%20we%20made%20the%20announcement.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20will%20talk%20to%20like-minded%20parties%20and%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20alliance%20when%20elections%20come%20near%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20dropped%20a%20major%20hint%2C%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bno%20party%20except%20the%20DMK%20is%20an%20opponent%26quot%3B%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20option%20of%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20is%20on%20the%20table.%20Another%20remark%2C%20however%2C%20indicated%20that%20while%20AIADMK%20may%20join%20forces%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20will%20only%20do%20so%20on%20its%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Palaniswami%20said%20AIADMK's%20stand%20on%20a%20two-language%20formula%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu%20students%20remains%20unchanged.%20%26quot%3BTwo-language%20(formula)%20has%20been%20the%20AIADMK's%20policy%20from%20the%20time%20of%20CN%20Annadurai%2C%20MGR%20and%20Amma%20(J%20Jayalalithaa).%20It%20should%20continue%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20underlining%20AIADMK's%20stand%20on%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20sparked%20a%20face-off%20between%20the%20DMK%20government%20and%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAIADMK-BJP%3A%20A%20Tale%20Of%20Reunions%20and%20Break-Ups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%20and%20BJP%20have%20a%20long%20history%20of%20electoral%20partnerships%2C%20chequered%20with%20several%20break-ups%20and%20patch-ups.%20In%20the%201998%20general%20election%2C%20the%20J%20Jayalalithaa-led%20party%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20scoring%2030%20out%20of%2039%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20however%2C%20AIADMK%20withdrew%20its%20support%20to%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%2C%20ostensibly%20after%20Mr%20Vajpayee%20refused%20to%20dismiss%20the%20DMK%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20A%20patch-up%20happened%20in%20the%202004%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20but%20while%20AIADMK%20won%20just%20one%20seat%2C%20the%20BJP%20scored%20a%20blank.%20At%20the%20Centre%2C%20the%20election%20marked%20an%20end%20to%20the%20NDA%20rule%20and%20the%20UPA%20returned%20to%20power.%20In%20the%20post-Jayalalithaa%20era%2C%20AIADMK%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202021%20state%20polls.%20The%20coalition%20managed%20to%20win%20just%2075%20seats%2C%20which%20DMK%20stormed%20to%20power%20with%20a%20score%20of%20159.%20This%20alliance%20fell%20through%20in%202023%20as%20state%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%20pushed%20hard%20to%20build%20a%20support%20base%20for%20the%20party%20and%20the%20AIADMK%20was%20not%20amused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20BJP%20contested%20separately%20and%20failed%20to%20open%20their%20accounts.%20The%20DMK%20again%20swept%20all%2039%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20AIADMK%20Dilemma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20E%20Palaniswami-led%20party%20has%20struggled%20to%20perform%20electorally%20since%20J%20Jayalalithaa's%20death%20in%20December%202016%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20infighting%20and%20lack%20of%20strong%20political%20messaging.%20Several%20key%20players%20in%20the%20state's%20politics%20are%20firmly%20with%20the%20DMK%2C%20forcing%20the%20AIADMK%20to%20look%20for%20partners.%20One%20such%20partner%20is%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20in%20a%20state%20with%20a%20history%20of%20Dravidian%20politics%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20largely%20viewed%20as%20a%20'North%20Indian%20party'%20and%20an%20alliance%20opens%20up%20AIADMK%20to%20the%20DMK's%20attacks%20in%20this%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20knows%20that%20an%20association%20with%20the%20BJP%20has%20rarely%20benefited%20it%20electorally.%20With%20the%20delimitation%20row%20and%20the%20third%20language%20issue%20raging%2C%20an%20association%20with%20the%20BJP%20may%20prove%20counter-productive%20for%20the%20main%20Opposition.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20will%20be%20mindful%20to%20prevent%20a%20division%20in%20the%20Opposition's%20votes%20to%20take%20on%20the%20DMK%20better.%20The%20BJP%20has%20improved%20its%20marginal%20presence%20in%20the%20state%20and%20hopes%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20popularity%20may%20better%20its%20poll%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20DMK%20government%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20state-controlled%20liquor%20trade%20after%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20started%20probing%20the%20case.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20many%20feel%20AIADMK%20may%20try%20to%20cozy%20up%20to%20the%20BJP%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20line%20of%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20alliance%20between%20AIADMK%20and%20BJP%20will%20be%20possible%20only%20if%20the%20two%20parties%20manage%20to%20navigate%20the%20complex%20web%20of%20local%20issues%20and%20national%20narratives%20and%20find%20a%20common%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743071220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F7vsftjro_eps-amit-shah_625x300_27_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-aiadmk-bjp-e-palaniswami-to-be-with-bjp-or-not-to-be-aiadmk-weighs-tamil-nadu-alliance-options-8023326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assembly%20polls%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20due%20next%20year%20and%20the%20key%20players%2C%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20and%20the%20main%20Opposition%20AIADMK%2C%20have%20started%20building%20their%20election%20planks%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-aiadmk-bjp-e-palaniswami-to-be-with-bjp-or-not-to-be-aiadmk-weighs-tamil-nadu-alliance-options-8023326%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20have%20the%20wildfires%20in%20S%20Korea%20been%20so%20devastating%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743071196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F365f%2Flive%2Fb8bc7fd0-0af2-11f0-88b7-5556e7b55c5e.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp8l60l8ppzo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Strong%20w