0offer%20to%20contract%20for%20them%2C%20it%20was%20an%20opportunity%20I%20couldn't%20pass%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recruiting%20manager%20from%20Apple%20messaged%20me%20on%20LinkedIn%20in%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20an%20impressive%20background.%20I%20oversee%20design%20and%20creative%20recruitment%20for%20Apple%20Media%20Products.%20I'm%20eager%20to%20see%20if%20I%20might%20be%20able%20to%20get%20you%20on%20the%20phone%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20at%20a%20convenient%20time%3F%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20hearing%20back!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20the%20role%20and%20worked%20at%20Apple%20for%20seven%20months%20%E2%80%94%20until%20they%20let%20go%20of%20over%20100%20contractors%2C%20including%20me.%20It%20wasn't%20the%20outcome%20I%20expected%2C%20but%20was%20a%20huge%20learning%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20with%20some%20of%20the%20best%20creative%20leaders%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20saw%20what%20top%20companies%20look%20for%20in%20talent%2C%20and%20learned%20to%20think%20beyond%20traditional%20recruiting%20tools.%20This%20experience%20made%20me%20a%20stronger%20recruiter%20and%20shaped%20how%20I%20help%20job%20seekers%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20having%20my%20LinkedIn%20profile%20optimized%20for%20the%20exact%20role%20I%20wanted%20was%20key%20to%20the%20recruiter%20finding%20me.%20Here's%20how%20I%20set%20it%20up%20and%20my%20advice%20for%20job%20seekers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a1e5fa5-54c4-4c00-ae19-f5ebd965b3a3%5C%22%3ECraft%20a%20compelling%20summary%20that%20tells%20your%20story%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20LinkedIn%20summary%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20recruiters%20look%20at%2C%20so%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20clear%20and%20impactful.%20I%20always%20recommend%20keeping%20it%20short%20%E2%80%94%20five%20to%20six%20sentences%20max.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20structuring%20it%20well%20is%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStart%20with%20who%20you%20are.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C