unprecedented%20in%2080%20years%26quot%3B.%20The%20transatlantic%20unity%20they%20had%20taken%20so%20much%20for%20granted%20had%20just%20been%20put%20on%20life%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDazed%20and%20desperate%2C%20a%20few%20European%20leaders%20even%20made%20a%20hasty%20pilgrimage%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20hoping%20to%20talk%20President%20Trump%20into%20letting%20them%20back%20into%20the%20negotiations.%20They%20pleaded%2C%20massaged%20his%20ego%20and%20no%20doubt%20spoke%20of%20shared%20values%20and%20historic%20bonds.%20Trump%2C%20in%20his%20signature%20style%2C%20didn't%20just%20refuse%E2%80%94he%20doubled%20down%2C%20showering%20praise%20on%20President%20Putin%20while%20the%20Europeans%20watched%2C%20horrified.%20And%20just%20when%20they%20thought%20things%20couldn't%20get%20worse%2C%20Trump's%20strategy%20became%20clear%3A%20push%20Ukraine%20into%20a%20ceasefire%20by%20any%20means%20necessary.%20Last%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20European%20Parliament%20responded%2C%20calling%20Washington's%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cblackmail%E2%80%9D.%20In%20an%20amusing%20twist%2C%20even%20some%20of%20the%20far-right%20MEPs%E2%80%94normally%20Trump's%20biggest%20cheerleaders%E2%80%94signed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20Europe%20had%20lived%20in%20the%20illusion%20that%20the%20US%20would%20always%20have%20its%20back.%20With%20NATO%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20they%20outsourced%20their%20security%20while%20their%20militaries%20withered%20away%20into%20underfunded%20relics.%20Now%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20hitting%20them%20hard%3A%20the%20transatlantic%20alliance%20isn't%20what%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%20and%20Europe%20might%20actually%20have%20to%20fend%20for%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20Timing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20once-mighty%20White%2C%20Western%20bloc%E2%80%94the%20self-proclaimed%20guardians%20of%20the%20post-WWII%20world%20order%E2%80%94is%20in%20disarray.%20And%20who%20ought%20to%20be%20watching%3F%20Indeed%20BRICS.%20The%20bloc%2C%20already%20an%20economic%20heavyweight%2C%20has%20grown%20even%20stronger%20since%20expanding%20to%2010%20members%20last%20year.%20Some%20in%20the%20West%20love%20to%20paint%20it%20as%20an%20anti-Western%20alliance%2C%20but%20that's%20wishful%20thinking.%20If%20anything%2C%20BRICS%20isn't%20trying%20to%20burn%20the%20house%20down%E2%80%94it%20just%20wants%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table.%20At%20its%20Kazan%20summit%20last%20October%2C%20it%20didn't%20call%20for%20tearing%20down%20the%20Bretton%20Woods%20institutions.%20Instead%2C%20it%20pushed%20for%20reforming%20them%2C%20making%20the%20global%20financial%20system%20fairer%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Russia%20and%20Iran%2C%20most%20BRICS%2B%20members%20maintain%20solid%20ties%20with%20the%20West.%20But%20the%20common%20thread%20binding%20them%3F%20A%20history%20of%20colonial%20exploitation%2C%20economic%20dependency%20and%20political%20meddling%E2%80%94courtesy%20of%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%20That%20shared%20past%20has%20given%20BRICS%20a%20purpose%3A%20challenging%20the%20entrenched%20dominance%20of%20Western%20powers%20and%20building%20what%20it%20calls%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20just%20and%20democratic%20world%20order%E2%80%9D.%20It%20may%20sound%20lofty%2C%20but%20with%20the%20West%20fumbling%20and%20bickering%2C%20BRICS%20must%20be%20seeing%20an%20opening.%20It%20must.%20From%20pushing%20for%20de-dollarisation%20to%20rejecting%20Western%20sanctions%2C%20the%20bloc%20is%20well-positioned%20as%20a%20possible%20counterweight%20to%20a%20system%20that%20has%20long%20favoured%20a%20select%20few.%20Indeed%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20the%20West%20wrote%20and%20imposed%20the%20rules.%20Now%2C%20BRICS%20must%20remind%20them%20that%20they%20are%20not%20the%20only%20players%20in%20the%20game.%20And%20may%20we%20emphasise%20that%20with%20the%20transatlantic%20alliance%20unravelling%2C%20the%20timing%20couldn't%20be%20better%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrike%20When%20The%20Iron%20Is%20Hot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20ready%20for%20it%20though%3F%20That's%20the%20billion-dollar%20question.%20Annoyingly%2C%20BRICS%2B%20only%20seems%20to%20make%20headlines%20during%20their%20annual%20summits%E2%80%94or%20when%20Trump%20threatens%20to%20slap%20them%20with%20sanctions.%20For%20a%20bloc%20that%20dreams%20of%20reshaping%20the%20global%20order%2C%20they%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20fading%20into%20the%20background%20when%20it%20actually%20matters.%20Even%20in%20their%20supposed%20area%20of%20strength%E2%80%94economy%E2%80%94they%20sometimes%20struggle%20to%20present%20a%20united%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20just%20look%20at%20their%20collective%20might%3A%20BRICS%2B%20represents%20a%20staggering%203.6%20billion%20people%2C%20nearly%2047%25%20of%20the%20world's%20population.%20Their%20economic%20weight%20is%2036%25%20of%20global%20GDP%20at%20purchasing%20power%20parity%20(PPP)%E2%80%94which%20is%20already%20surpassing%20the%20G7's%2030%25.%20And%20while%20the%20West%20loves%20to%20scoff%20at%20BRICS%2B%2C%20analysts%20in%20Washington%20and%20Brussels%20are%20feeling%20uneasy.%20Why%3F%20Because%20by%202050%2C%20BRICS%2B%20economies%20are%20projected%20to%20control%2050%25%20of%20global%20wealth%20production%2C%20while%20the%20G7%20will%20shrink%20to%2020%25.%20The%20numbers%20only%20get%20more%20intimidating%3A%20BRICS%2B%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%2038.3%25%20of%20global%20industrial%20production%2C%2025%25%20of%20global%20goods%20exports%2C%20and%20already%20commands%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20global%20infrastructure%20investments.%20They%20dominate%20the%20energy%20sector%20too%2C%20with%2054%25%20of%20global%20oil%20production%2C%2053%25%20of%20natural%20gas%20reserves%2C%2040%25%20of%20coal%20reserves%2C%20and%20nearly%20half%20of%20global%20food%20production.%20And%20lastly%2C%20these%20nations%20are%20also%20poised%20to%20control%20the%20world's%20critical%20minerals%20and%20strategic%20metals%2C%20which%20are%20vital%20for%20the%20much-hyped%20energy%20transition%20and%20advanced%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20staggering%20economic%20strength%2C%20BRICS%2B%20nations%20still%20play%20the%20role%20of%20petitioners%20in%20global%20financial%20institutions%2C%20politely%20knocking%20on%20doors%20controlled%20by%20the%20West.%20One%20of%20their%20supposed%20core%20objectives%20is%20to%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20and%20World%20Bank%2C%20institutions%20long%20accused%20of%20imposing%20neoliberal%20policies%20that%20prioritise%20Western%20economic%20interests%20over%20those%20of%20developing%20nations.%20Sounds%20noble%2C%20but%20when%20the%20time%20comes%20to%20make%20bold%20moves%2C%20BRICS%2B%20has%20been%20known%20to%20dither.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Russia's%20Finance%20Minister%20Anton%20Siluanov%2C%20who%2C%20fresh%20off%20the%20Kazan%20summit%2C%20actually%20showed%20some%20backbone.%20He%20called%20for%20a%20BRICS%20alternative%20to%20the%20IMF%20and%20World%20Bank%2C%20complete%20with%20its%20own%20rating%20agency%20and%20commodities%20exchange.%20The%20response%20from%20other%20BRICS%20finance%20ministers%20and%20central%20bank%20chiefs%20was%20at%20best%20vague.%20Indeed%2C%20they%20have%20the%20New%20Development%20Bank%20(NDB)%2C%20which%20offers%20loans%20without%20Washington-style%20political%20strings%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20they're%20increasingly%20trading%20in%20local%20currencies%20to%20reduce%20reliance%20on%20the%20US%20dollar.%20Russia%20and%20China%20even%20built%20CIPS%2C%20their%20answer%20to%20SWIFT%2C%20to%20bypass%20Western%20financial%20chokeholds.%20But%20the%20moment%20Trump%20pushed%20back%20on%20de-dollarisation%2C%20BRICS%20nations%20scrambled%20to%20clarify%E2%80%94'oh%20no%2C%20we%20aren't%20replacing%20the%20dollar%2C%20just%E2%80%A6%20exploring%20options'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhich%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20real%20question%20at%20hand.%20We%20all%20know%20how%20power%20works%3A%20whoever%20controls%20the%20economic%20levers%20gets%20to%20write%20the%20rules%2C%20set%20the%20policies%20and%20dictate%20the%20political%20agenda.%20The%20G7%20isn't%20running%20the%20show%20just%20because%20it's%20rich%E2%80%94it%20is%20because%20it%20dominates%20the%20geopolitical%20chessboard%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20BRICS%20faces%20this%20challenge%3A%20can%20it%20turn%20its%20economic%20muscle%20into%20real%20political%20influence%3F%20Right%20now%2C%20as%20I%20said%20at%20the%20outset%2C%20the%20Western-led%20order%20is%20more%20fractured%20than%20ever%2C%20plagued%20by%20trans-Atlantic%20divisions%20and%20waning%20global%20dominance.%20This%20should%20be%20BRICS'%20moment%20to%20step%20up.%20But%20if%20it%20keeps%20tiptoeing%20around%20the%20big%20fights%20and%20avoiding%20the%20messy%20realities%20of%20global%20power%20struggles%2C%20it%20risks%20becoming%20nothing%20more%20than%20a%20high-powered%20trade%20club%E2%80%94economically%20formidable%20but%20politically%20almost%20irrelevant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20obvious%20examples%20of%20BRICS%2B%20either%20staying%20silent%20or%20missing%20in%20action%20on%20major%20global%20flashpoints%E2%80%94moments%20where%20it%20could%20have%20asserted%20itself%20but%20instead%20chose%20to%20watch%20from%20the%20sidelines%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20the%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20regime%20was%20toppled%20by%20the%20Islamist%20militant%20group%20Hayat%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%2C%20led%20by%20Ahmed%20al-Sharaa%2C%20the%20US%20and%20European%20powers%20wasted%20no%20time%20in%20reshaping%20Syria's%20future%20to%20their%20liking.%20They%20propped%20up%20al-Sharaa's%20makeshift%20coalition%20and%20started%20carving%20out%20their%20own%20version%20of%20%26quot%3Bstability%26quot%3B.%20BRICS%20nations%20were%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen%E2%80%94either%20collectively%20or%20individually.%20This%20was%20a%20textbook%20opportunity%20to%20step%20in%20as%20a%20counterweight%20to%20Western%20interventionism%2C%20perhaps%20even%20play%20mediator.%20After%20all%2C%20Syria%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJust%20last%20week%2C%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20in%20a%20stunningly%20undiplomatic%20move%2C%20announced%20on%20social%20media%20that%20South%20Africa's%20ambassador%20had%2072%20hours%20to%20pack%20up%20and%20leave.%20No%20warning%2C%20no%20justification%20beyond%20vague%20accusations%20that%20the%20ambassador%20was%20anti-American%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETrump%20has%20often%20accused%20South%20Africa%20of%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminating%26quot%3B%20against%20its%20White%20minority%20and%20offered%20the%20%26quot%3Bpersecuted%26quot%3B%20ones%20US%20citizenship.%20%C2%A0Observers%20suspect%20the%20real%20reason%3A%20South%20Africa%20had%20dared%20to%20take%20Israel%20to%20the%20ICC%20last%20year.%20Or%20whatever%20was%20the%20reason%2C%20no%20BRICS%2B%20spoke%20a%20word%20in%20favour%20of%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20bloc%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThen%20there's%20Ukraine.%20While%20President%20Trump%20has%20positioned%20himself%20as%20the%20main%20pacemaker%2C%20Europe%20has%20been%20banging%20the%20war%20drums%2C%20peddling%20fear%20over%20Russia.%20Here%20was%20BRICS%2B's%20moment%20to%20step%20in%2C%20offer%20mediation%20and%20bolster%20Trump's%20peace%20stance%E2%80%94something%20he%20would%20likely%20have%20welcomed%2C%20given%20the%20relentless%20pressure%20from%20European%20leaders%20and%20media.%20Instead%2C%20BRICS%2B%20is%20letting%20the%20opportunity%20slip%2C%20watching%20the%20geopolitical%20development%20from%20the%20sidelines.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20not%20just%20isolated%20incidents%2C%20they%20are%20proof%20of%20a%20pattern%E2%80%94one%20where%20BRICS%2B%20boasts%20economic%20strength%20but%20repeatedly%20fails%20to%20flex%20its%20geopolitical%20muscle%20when%20it%20actually%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Geopolitical%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20hostility%20towards%20BRICS%20is%20no%20secret.%20His%20%E2%80%9CAmerica%20First%E2%80%9D%20doctrine%20shuns%20multilateralism%20and%20he%20has%20openly%20criticised%20China%20and%20Russia%E2%80%94two%20of%20BRICS'%20quite%20influential%20members.%20After%20returning%20to%20the%20White%20House%20in%20January%2C%20Trump%20has%20started%20to%20put%20more%20pressure%20on%20BRICS%20nations%20through%20economic%20restrictions%20and%20trade%20war%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20question%20isn't%20what%20Trump%20wants%20to%20do.%20It's%20what%20BRICS%20will%20do.%20Can%20the%20bloc%20respond%20with%20a%20unified%20political%20strategy%2C%20or%20will%20it%20continue%20to%20be%20little%20more%20than%20an%20economic%20collective%20that%20carries%20less%20than%20deserved%20weight%20on%20the%20world%20stage%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Coherent%20Force%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20so%20far%2C%20BRICS%20has%20struggled%20to%20project%20itself%20as%20a%20coherent%20geopolitical%20force.%20Unlike%20NATO%20or%20the%20G7%2C%20BRICS%20lacks%20a%20common%20security%20framework%2C%20leaving%20it%20as%20an%20economic%20heavyweight%20with%20no%20military%20or%20diplomatic%20backbone.%20It%20has%20also%20failed%20to%20act%20decisively%20in%20global%20crises%2C%20making%20it%20appear%20passive%20rather%20than%20proactive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20good%20enough.%20Doubling%20up%20on%20de-dollarisation%20efforts%2C%20strengthening%20the%20New%20Development%20Bank%20and%20forming%20strategic%20partnerships%20within%20the%20bloc%20could%20increase%20its%20clout.%20But%20it's%20certain%20that%20without%20political%20will%2C%20these%20remain%20just%20well-intentioned%20ambitions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20cautious%20leaders%20and%20seasoned%20diplomats%20may%20disagree%2C%20but%20if%20BRICS%20wants%20to%20be%20taken%20seriously%2C%20it%20must%20step%20up%20as%