ties%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20types%20of%20extreme%20weather%20have%20a%20well-established%20link%20with%20climate%20change%2C%20such%20as%20heatwaves%20or%20heavy%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20phenomena%2C%20such%20as%20forest%20fires%2C%20droughts%2C%20snowstorms%20and%20tropical%20storms%20can%20result%20from%20a%20combination%20of%20complex%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20wildfire%20has%20once%20again%20exposed%20the%20harsh%20reality%20of%20a%20climate%20crisis%20unlike%20anything%20we've%20experienced%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20disaster%20chief%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20affected%20areas%20have%20seen%20only%20half%20the%20average%20rainfall%2C%20coupled%20with%20unusually%20strong%20winds%2C%20which%20have%20drastically%20accelerated%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20fire%20and%20intensified%20the%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeh%20Sang-Wook%2C%20professor%20of%20climatology%20at%20Seoul's%20Hanyang%20University%2C%20told%20AFP%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20rainfall%20had%20dried%20out%20the%20land%20%26quot%3Bcreating%20favourable%20conditions%20for%20wildfires.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20say%20that%20it's%20only%20due%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20but%20climate%20change%20is%20directly%20(and)%20indirectly%20affecting%20the%20changes%20we%20are%20experiencing%20now.%20This%20is%20a%20sheer%20fact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20another%20expert%2C%20professor%20Hong%20Suk-hwan%20at%20Pusan%20National%20University's%20Department%20of%20Landscape%20Architecture%2C%20said%20the%20country's%20forest%20management%20practices%20also%20took%20some%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea%20has%20prioritised%20the%20preservation%20of%20large%20pine%20trees%20--%20packed%20with%20oily%20resin%20--%20above%20allowing%20a%20variety%20of%20deciduous%20trees%20to%20thrive%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20fire%20breaks%20out%2C%20would%20it%20spread%20more%20easily%20on%20wet%20paper%20or%20on%20dry%20paper%20soaked%20in%20oil%3F%20Our%20forests%20are%20essentially%20covered%20in%20oil-soaked%20paper%2C%20creating%20an%20environment%20where%20wildfires%20can%20spread%20at%20an%20alarming%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWere%20South%20Korea%20to%20have%20cultivated%20more%20deciduous%20trees%20in%20a%20natural%20mixed%20forest%20it%20%26quot%3Bwould%20slow%20wildfire%20spread%20and%20prevent%20it%20from%20escalating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAncient%20Pines%20Cut%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20200-year-old%20pine%20tree%20at%20Bongjeongsa%20temple%20in%20Andong%20--%20the%20oldest%20wooden%20structure%20in%20South%20Korea%20and%20a%20UNESCO-listed%20site%20--%20was%20cut%20down%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20preserve%20the%20temple%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20cut%20it%20down...%20The%20fire%20is%20spreading%20rapidly%20from%20one%20pine%20tree%20to%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20monk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20UNESCO-listed%20Byeongsan%20Seowon%2C%20a%20former%20Confucian%20academy%2C%20the%20sky%20was%20hazy%2C%20AFP%20reporters%20saw%2C%20with%20fire%20trucks%20spraying%20water%20and%20fire%20retardants%20onto%20the%20historic%20site%20in%20a%20desperate%20bid%20to%20save%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20spraying%20three%20tonnes%20of%20water%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20Seung-myung%20from%20the%20Andong%20fire%20department%20told%20AFP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoi%20Young-ho%2C%20a%20firefighter%20at%20the%20heritage%20site%2C%20said%20that%20they%20were%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20wind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20wind%2C%20it%20will%20carry%20flames%20from%20afar%20--%20a%20very%20worrisome%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERain%20is%20forecast%20for%20late%20Thursday%2C%20potentially%20giving%20authorities%20a%20much-needed%20window%20to%20extinguish%20the%20blazes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743067380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Falnb14ro_south-korea-wildfire_625x300_27_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-korea-wildfires-largest-on-record-27-dead-8022946%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wildfires%20in%20South%20Korea%20are%20now%20the%20largest%20and%20deadliest%20on%20record%2C%20having%20burned%20more%20forest%20and%20killed%20more%20people%20than%20any%20previous%20blaze%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20as%20the%20deaths%20hit%2027.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-korea-wildfires-largest-on-record-27-dead-8022946%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rashmika%20Mandanna%20reveals%20her%20favorite%20Korean%20and%20Chinese%20dramas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743067312000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119587658%2Cimgsize-814845.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frashmika-mandanna-suggests-these-must-watch-k-dramas-and-c-dramas-to-fans-picking-its-okay-to-not-be-okay-as-her-favorite%2Farticleshow%2F119587730.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119587730.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERashmika%20Mandanna%20engaged%20with%20fans%20on%20Instagram%20after%20a%20break%2C%20sharing%20her%20favorite%20Korean%20and%20Chinese%20dramas%20like%20'Love%20Scout%2C'%20'The%20First%20Frost%2C'%20and%20'The%20Undercover%20High%20School.'%20She%20also%20ment