%20list%20of%20central%20contracts%20for%20this%20year%20yet%20and%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Dainik%20Jagran%2C%20it%20can%20have%20some%20big%20news%20for%20the%20senior%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20The%20report%20claimed%20that%20discussions%20regarding%20the%20BCCI%20central%20contracts%20will%20take%20place%20during%20the%20high-profile%20meeting%20on%20March%2029%20in%20Guwahati.%20While%20the%20India%20squad%20for%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20England%20will%20be%20top%20priority%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20central%20contracts%20are%20also%20reportedly%20on%20the%20agenda.%20The%20report%20further%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20selection%20committee%20is%20divided%20about%20the%20future%20of%20some%20of%20India's%20big%20stars%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20new%20list%20may%20carry%20surprises%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20future%20of%20the%20stars%20will%20become%20clearer%20following%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20report%20by%20Times%20Of%20India%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20may%20end%20up%20losing%20out%20on%20their%20Grade%20A%2B%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20claimed%20that%20players%20who%20excel%20in%20all%20three%20formats%20are%20given%20preference%20for%20Grade%20A%2B%20contracts%20and%20the%20trio's%20retirement%20from%20the%20T20%20format%20has%20complicated%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5