E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20advantages%20of%20her%20system%20is%20its%20ease%20of%20installation.%20%E2%80%9CMannat%E2%80%99s%20design%20does%20not%20involve%20changes%20in%20their%20household%E2%80%99s%20existing%20plumbing%20systems%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20fit%20and%20economical%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gurneet%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20also%20customise%20the%20buckets%20according%20to%20the%20individual%E2%80%99s%20aesthetic%20appeal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mannat%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMannat%20is%20now%20focused%20on%20making%20her%20system%20commercially%20available.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20go%20ahead%2C%20I%20hope%20to%20make%20it%20into%20a%20product%20that%20can%20be%20brought%20off%20the%20shelf%2C%20and%20those%20are%20the%20next%20proceedings%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20hoping%20to%20do%20through%20fellowships%20I%E2%80%99m%20taking%20part%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20vision%20is%20to%20empower%20households%20to%20take%20control%20of%20their%20water%20usage%20and%20contribute%20to%20a%20more%20sustainable%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMannat%20Kaur%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20an%20inspiring%20example%20of%20how%20youthful%20innovation%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20real-world%20problems%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20impactful%20solutions.%20Her%20greywater%20recycling%20system%20addresses%20water%20scarcity%20and%20promotes%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle%2C%20making%20her%20a%20true%20champion%20of%20environmental%20stewardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Megha%20Chowdhury%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Mannat%20Kaur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742806800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fgreywater-recycling-1742798018.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D415415%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%