rly%20two%20decades.%20Founded%20in%202007%20by%20Pooja%20Taparia%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20developed%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20prevention%2C%20education%2C%20and%20healing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Taparia%20had%20a%20moment%20that%20changed%20everything.%20%E2%80%9CI%20watched%20the%20play%20named%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E30%20Days%20in%20September%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20understood%20the%20lasting%20trauma%20that%20can%20be%20experienced%20by%20adult%20survivors%20of%20childhood%20sexual%20abuse.%20It%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20do%20something%20through%20my%20organisation%20to%20help.%20I%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20education%20and%20prevention%20to%20stop%20this%20abuse%20from%20happening%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201156px)%20100vw%2C%201156px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FIMG-20250301-WA0009-1-1742568966.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20goal%20of%20Arpan%20NGO%20is%20to%20provide%20children%20with%20the%20knowledge%20to%20say%20%E2%80%98no%E2%80%99%20when%20they%20face%20unsafe%20situations%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FIMG-20250301-WA0009-1-1742568966.jpg%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FIMG-20250301-WA0009-1-1742568966-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FIMG-20250301-WA0009-1-1742568966-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2